quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,6,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe foti a jeertinii …ďe wolla a jeertinaani, fof foti he mum ma…ď…ďe."
  2,7,"Alla muppi …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, wirngallo woni e noppi e gite ma…ď…ďe lette maw…óe na woodani …ďe."
  2,8,"Na woodi heen yim…ďe wi'oo…ďe min ngoong…óinii Alla e √Īalaande wattan, tawa …ďe ngoong…óinaani."
  2,9,"E…ďe koda Alla e goong…óin…ďe …ďe, alaa mbo …ďe kodata so wonaa ko'e ma…ď…ďe tawa …ďe tinaani."
  2,10,"Ko √Īawu woni he …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, Alla …ďeydani …ďe √Īawu , maa lette muus…óe njan he mum en sabu ko …ďe penannoo."
  2,11,"So …ďe mbi'aama hoto mbonnee he lesdi ndii …ďe mbi'a minen ko min mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe."
  2,12,"Ko kam…ďe tigi ngoni bonnoo…ďe kono …ďe tinataa …óum."
  2,13,"So …ďe mbi'aama ngoong…óinee wano yim…ďe …ďee ngoong…óiniri nii, …ďe mbi'a mbela min ngoong…óinat wano …óaay…ďe …ďee ngoong…óiniri nii, kono ko kam…ďe tigi ngoni …óaay…ďe kono …ďe nganndaa."
  2,14,"So tawii …ďe kawrii he goon…óin…ďe …ďee, …ďe mbi'a: min ngoong…óinii, so …ďe njeewdii e sey…óanooji ma…ď…ďe …óii …ďe mbi'a: minen ko onon min ngonndi min njalkitat tan."
  2,15,"Alla na jalkita …ďe O …ďeydana …ďe bewre …ďe ngona e wemmbere."
  2,16,"Ko …ďeen ngoni soodir…ďe peewal majjere njulaagu ma…ď…ďe alaa tono, te …ďe peewaano."